(1, 'DashboardPage', '2018-05-07 21:26:36', '2017-09-25 06:18:29', 'home', 'Home', NULL, '<p>Welcome to SilverStripe! This is the default homepage. You can edit this page by opening <a href=\"admin/\">the CMS</a>.</p><p>You can now access the <a href=\"http://docs.silverstripe.org\">developer documentation</a>, or begin the <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/learn/lessons\">SilverStripe lessons</a>.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 6, 0),
(2, 'Page', '2017-11-24 11:39:54', '2017-09-25 06:18:29', 'about', 'About', NULL, '<p>Our mission here at Honest Day\'s Work is to provide you the opportunities you need to create your own lifestyle. In essence this means creating an open market where people can use the skills they have to find the work they want. Jump off the 9 to 5 treadmill and contract your skills out!</p><p> </p><p>We also aim to make it easier to get work done. Got 10 jobs to do, but haven\'t got the time to be ringing around chasing prices? Honest Day\'s Work provides a simple and powerful platform for you to present your jobs to the people with the right skills for the work.</p><p> </p><p><a title=\"Frequently Asked Questions\" href=\"[sitetree_link,id=12]\">FAQ\'s</a></p><p><a href=\"[sitetree_link,id=3]\">Feedback</a></p><p><a title=\"Resources for Preparing Tenders\" href=\"[sitetree_link,id=16]\">Resources for Preparing Tenders</a></p><p><a title=\"Resources for Submitting Tenders\" href=\"[sitetree_link,id=17]\">Resources for Submitting Tenders</a></p><p><a href=\"[sitetree_link,id=13]\">Terms and Conditions</a></p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 5, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 14, 0),
(3, 'Page', '2018-01-26 14:09:34', '2017-09-25 06:18:29', 'contact', 'Feedback', NULL, '<p>We\'d love to hear what you think about Honest Day\'s Work.</p><p>Click the link below to provide feedback:</p><p><a title=\"Feedback\" href=\"mailto:admin@honestdayswork.nz?subject=Feedback\">admin@honestdayswork.nz</a> </p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 6, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 10, 2),
