t you. After 3 such complaints, Honest Day\'s Work may suspend or terminate your membership.</p><p> </p><p>4.3 Your obligations as a buyer</p><p> </p><p>You must be located in New Zealand or Australia to buy on Honest Day\'s Work. People outside of these countries are not permitted to create tenders on Honest Day\'s Work.</p><p> </p><p>Tenders are not pre-screened for content. Honest Day\'s Work reserves the right to remove any tender that it deems unsuitable or in breach of the terms and conditions.</p><p> </p><p>You agree to your email address being provided to the tenderers when your tender closes.</p><p> </p><p>You must make full and prompt payment for any item you buy, or as may be otherwise described in the contract agreement.</p><p> </p><p>If you do not pay for the contract as requried by the contract documents or the contract agreement, you will receive a warning from Honest Day\'s Work if the seller complains about you. After 3 such complaints, Honest Day\'s Work may suspend or terminate your membership.</p><p> </p><p>4.4 Feedback</p><p> </p><p>Feedback is provided for the purpose of facilitating trading between members on the Honest Day\'s Work Website. Feedback you provide on other members must not contain offensive, defamatory, retaliatory or inappropriate language or content. Honest Day\'s Work may remove any feedback that we consider to be offensive, defamatory, retaliatory or inappropriate.</p><p> </p><p>You may only give member feedback that relates to a specific transaction. You must not post feedback on a transaction that does not relate to that specific transaction.</p><p> </p><p>You must not post feedback about yourself or include any contact details or personal information in your feedback.</p><p> </p><p>FEES AND ACCOUNTS</p><p> </p><p>5.1 Honest Day\'s Work Listing Fees and Success Fees</p><p> </p><p>Honest Day\'s Work charges fees for the use of the Website as a venue.</p><p> </p><p>Honest Day\'s Work\'s current fees are listed on our fees page in the FAQ section.</p><p> </p><p>Any non-commission listing fees are charged at the time of listing and are not refundable.</p><p> </p><p>Honest Day\'s Work reserves the right to change the fees charged for any of our Services at any time. In the event that we introduce a new Service, the fees for that Service are effective at the launch of the Service, unless otherwise stated.</p><p> </p><p>If you are a New Zealand resident, then all fees are inclusive of GST and in New Zealand dollars unless otherwise stated. If you are not a New Zealand resident, then all fees are, unless otherwise stated, in New Zealand dollars and do not include GST. Unless otherwise stated in these terms and conditions, no interest or other financial charges will be applied to Honest Day\'s Work account balances.</p><p> </p><p>Honest Day\'s Work reserves the right to investigate queries regarding the refund of success fees with bidders, other members and any other relevant party.</p><p> </p><p>Before listing a tender, you should review Honest Day\'s Work\'s fees to ensure you are aware of the fees that you will incur.</p><p> </p><p>You must pay the fees immediately upon demand by Honest Day\'s Work.</p><p> </p><p>GENERAL PROVISIONS</p><p> </p><p>6.1 System Integrity: Honest Day\'s Work will use its reasonable endeavours to ensure the availability of the Website and Services, subject to any downtime required for maintenance. However, Honest Day\'s Work takes no responsibility for any system unavailability, or for any loss that is incurred as a result of Website or Services being unavailable. Further, Honest Day\'s Work assumes no responsibility for the corruption of any data or information held by Honest Day\'s Work.</p><p> </p><p>6.2 Resolution of disputes: As Honest Day\'s Work is not a party to any sale or transaction between you and another member, you agree not to involve, or attempt to involve, Honest Day\'s Work in any dispute or in the resolution of disputes that arise between you an