 Work;</p><p>\'Services\' means any one or more of the services offered by Honest Day\'s Work Limited from time to time, including online tenders, classifieds, message boards, sms alerts and any other service that Honest Day\'s Work may offer;</p><p>\'we\', \'us\' and \'our\' are a reference to Honest Day\'s Work Limited;</p><p>\'you\' and \'your\' are a reference to you;</p><p>\'Website\' means any Honest Day\'s Work website through which the services are offered;</p><p>\'purchaser\' includes any person placing a listing;</p><p>\'seller\' includes any person submitting tender proposals</p><p> </p><p>SPECIFIC WARNINGS</p><p> </p><p>2.1 The Services: Honest Day\'s Work provides a venue to introduce members who want to negioate contracts. Honest Day\'s Work does not take any part in the purachse or sale of services, products or contracts other than by providing our Website as a venue for members. If a contract is accepted by a purchaser, a contract will be formed between the buyer and the seller directly. We do not act as agent for either party and do not participate in any purchase, sale or transaction between you and other members.</p><p> </p><p>2.2 At your own risk: Transactions and all other contact between you and other members are conducted entirely at your own risk. You agree that Honest Day\'s Work takes no responsibility or liability for any misconduct of any of its members including, without limitation, members that have registered under false pretences or who attempt to defraud you. Honest Day\'s Work gives no undertakings, representations, or warranties in relation to contracts tendered, listed or awarded on the Website including:as to the content, safety, description, worthiness, quality, or legality of the contracts or services that are procured on the Website; as to the accuracy or truth of tender details; that any tender sumbmitted or awarded will meet your requirements or expectations; or about the ability of members to complete a transaction.</p><p> 