(50, 13, 7, 1, 2, 2, 'Page', '2017-10-27 14:55:39', '2017-10-27 12:43:22', 'terms-and-conditions', 'Terms and Conditions', NULL, '<h3>Terms and conditions, last updated 15 September 2017</h3><p> </p><p>Honest Day\'s Work terms and conditions are here to ensure this is a safe place to buy and sell services.</p><p> </p><p>1.1 Amendment of terms and conditions: As Honest Day\'s Work operates in a changing commercial, technological and regulatory environment, we may amend these terms and conditions from time to time. We will communicate all changes by Site Announcement. We will generally give you at least two weeks’ notice to review these changes. Unless otherwise stated, amendments will be effective immediately upon posting of the amended terms and conditions on the Honest Day\'s Work website. It is your responsibility to ensur you are familiar with the latest terms and conditions. Your continued use of the Services represents your agreement to the amended terms and conditions.</p><p> </p><p>1.2 Terminology: In these terms and conditions, the following expressions have the meanings set out:</p><p> </p><p>\'tender\' includes both \'open tenders\' and \'closed tenders\' and refers to a listing on the website which you purchase, negioate, offer, buy, sell or advertise any service or product or contract to perform work;</p><p>\'open tender\' refers to a tender which any member of Honest Day\'s Work may subit a proposal;</p><p>\'closed tender\' refers to a tender which only menbers of Honest Day\'s Work who have been invited by the tenderer may submit submissions;</p><p>\'tender submisson\' refers to offers from sellers to complete the work as described in the tender documentation, including the tender notices during the tender period;</p><p>\'Contract\' refers to the agreement between the buyer and the selected tenderer to have the work completed to the agreed standard and extent and timeframe for the agreed cost.</p><p>\'member\' means a registered member of Honest Day\'s Work;</p><p>\'Services\' means any one or more of the services offered by Honest Day\'s Work Limited from time to time, including online tenders, classifieds, message boards, sms alerts and any other service that Honest Day\'s Work may offer;</p><p>\'we\', \'us\' and \'our\' are a reference to Honest Day\'s Work Limited;</p><p>\'you\' and \'your\' are a reference to you;</p><p>\'Website\' means any Honest Day\'s Work website through which the services are offered;</p><p>\'purchaser\' includes any person placing a listing;</p><p>\'seller\' includes any person submitting tender proposals</p><p> </p><p>SPECIFIC WARNINGS</p><p> </p><p>2.1 The Services: Honest Day\'s Work provides a venue to introduce members who want to negioate contracts. Honest Day\'s Work does not take any part in the purachse or sale of services, products or contracts other than by providing our Website as a venue for members. If a contract is accepted by a purchaser, a contract will be formed between the buyer and the seller directly. We do not act as agent for either party and do not participate in any purchase, sale or transaction between you and other members.</p><p> </p><p>2.2 At your own risk: Transactions and all other contact between you and other members are conducted entirely at your own risk. You agree that Honest Day\'s Work takes no responsibility or liability for any misconduct of any of its members including, without limitation, members that have registered under false pretences or who attempt to defraud you. Honest Day\'s Work gives no undertakings, representations, or warranties in relation to contracts tendered, listed or awarded on the Website including: the content, safety, description, worthiness, quality, or legality of the contracts or services that are procured on the Website; the accuracy or truth of tender details; that any tender sumbmitted or awarded will meet your requirements or expectations; or about the ability of members to complete a transaction.</p><p> </p><p> </p