sell any information, or items obtained from any part of this Website.</p><p> </p><p>6.8 Entire agreement: These terms and conditions supersede all previous conditions, understandings, commitments, agreements and representations whatsoever whether oral or written, and constitutes the entire agreement, between the parties, relating to the subject matter of these terms and conditions.</p><p> </p><p>ACCEPTANCE</p><p> </p><p>7.1 Acceptance of terms and conditions: The terms and conditions are the terms on which Honest Day\'s Work Limited offers you access to the Services and the Website. By registering as a member of Honest Day\'s Work you accept these terms and conditions and will adhear to them.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 13, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 8),
