(130, 18, 7, 0, 2, 0, 'Page', '2017-11-19 14:48:03', '2017-11-17 11:11:24', 'pricing-structure', 'Cost', NULL, '<p><strong>Creating a Tender</strong></p><p> - For simple tenders - <strong>Free</strong> (see below for a description of simple tenders)</p><p> - For complex tenders - $1 per feature up to a maximum of $8.</p><p> The list of possible features is:</p><p>      - Estimate</p><p>      - Schedule of Prices</p><p>      - Specifications</p><p>      - Drawings/Sketch</p><p>      - Terms of Payment</p><p>      - Standard Conditions</p><p>      - Special Conditions</p><p>      - Conditions of Tendering</p><p> </p><p><strong>Submitting a Tender</strong></p><p> - For simple tenders - $1 per submission</p><p> - For complex tenders - $1 per feature uploaded during setup. The cost will be the same as the setup cost.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 17, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0),
