ell or advertise any service or product or contract to perform work or request work;</p><p>\'Open tender\' refers to a tender which any member of Honest Day\'s Work may submit a proposal;</p><p>\'Closed tender\' refers to a tender which only members of Honest Day\'s Work who have been invited by the Client may submit submissions;</p><p>‘Client or Purchaser’ refers to the registered member who has listed a tender on Honest Day’s Work.</p><p>‘Contractor or Seller’ refers to the registered member who has submitted a Proposal on Honest Day’s Work.</p><p>‘Proposal’ refers to an offer to complete a service or provide a product or complete a job for a sum of money.</p><p>\'Tender submission\' refers to offers from sellers to complete the work as described in the tender documentation, including the tender notices during the tender period;</p><p>\'Contract\' refers to the agreement between the buyer and the selected tenderer to have the work completed to the agreed standard and extent and timeframe for the agreed cost.</p><p>\'Member\' means a registered user of Honest Day\'s Work;</p><p>\'Services\' means any one or more of the services offered by Honest Day\'s Work Limited, including online tenders, classifieds, and any other service that Honest Day\'s Work may offer;</p><p>\'Website\' means any Honest Day\'s Work website through which the services are offered;</p><p> </p><p>8 Law</p><p>These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of New Zealand. You submit to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the Courts of New Zealand.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 13, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 8),
